tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ARObjectInteractions (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    object_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE AR_Object_Interactions (
  interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  ar_object_id UUID,
  user_id UUID,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE User_Analytics (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  ar_object_id UUID,
  total_interactions INT,
  last_interaction_date DATE,
  avg_time_per_interaction INTERVAL,
  total_time_interacting INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE Performance_Analysis (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  session_duration INTERVAL,
  interaction_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE ar_interactions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ar_object_id INT NOT NULL,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  interaction_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE ar_objects (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  object_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE user_analytics (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  session_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_count INT NOT NULL,
  last_interaction_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE performance_analysis (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ar_object_id INT NOT NULL,
  render_time_ms INT NOT NULL,
  frame_rate FLOAT NOT NULL,
  analysis_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    ar_object_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE performance_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    ar_object_id INT,
    performance_metric VARCHAR(50),
    metric_value DECIMAL(10,2),
    analysis_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_start_time TIMESTAMP,
    session_end_time TIMESTAMP,
    total_interactions_during_session INT
);
